# TDD Required

This project expects TDD for new functionality.

- When adding a new file for a feature, add or update tests in the same change.
- Prefer writing the relevant test first, then implementation, then refactor.
- Rails controllers/services use Minitest under `test/`.
- Vue pages/components use Vitest under `app/frontend/tests/` or existing frontend test folders.
- Do not report a feature as complete without saying which tests were added or updated and which commands passed.

Before committing, keep unrelated dirty files out of the commit.
